PostGIS dependency prefix.

Target triple: @TARGET_TRIPLE@
Target kind: @TARGET_KIND@

Base packages:
- GDAL @GDAL_VERSION@
- CGAL @CGAL_VERSION@
- SFCGAL @SFCGAL_VERSION@

Additional dependency sources:
- libmd @LIBMD_VERSION@
- libbsd @LIBBSD_VERSION@
- Qhull @QHULL_VERSION@
- protobuf @PROTOBUF_VERSION@
- protobuf-c @PROTOBUF_C_VERSION@

This prefix is intended as the reusable dependency SDK for building PostGIS.
It intentionally does not contain PostgreSQL, libpq, pg_config, or PostGIS
itself; those are combined in the PostGIS package step.
